# Agent executes — don't delegate (RL-0051)

**Standing order (Avery 2026-06-16):** If it does not violate an explicit user rule or require **sudo**, **just do it.**

Execute: git hygiene, SSH DGX, `make forge-push`, verify, branch cleanup, ledger updates. Use `cd /path/to/repo && …` — never instruct operator to cd from `~`.

**Boss Moves ONLY:** sudo · secrets · browser test · explicit don't-commit/push · force-push main

